# 4. Conditional Statements

## if

```javascript
if(age >= 18){
    console.log("Eligible");
}
```

---

## if-else

```javascript
if(age >= 18){
    console.log("Eligible");
}else{
    console.log("Not Eligible");
}
```

---

## else-if

```javascript
if(marks >= 90){
    console.log("A");
}else if(marks >= 75){
    console.log("B");
}else{
    console.log("C");
}
```

---

## switch

```javascript
switch(day){
    case 1:
        console.log("Monday");
        break;

    default:
        console.log("Invalid");
}
```

### break

Stops execution of further cases.

