# 5. Loops

Used to repeat tasks.

---

## for Loop

```javascript
for(let i = 1; i <= 5; i++){
    console.log(i);
}
```

Output:

```javascript
1
2
3
4
5
```

---

## while Loop

```javascript
let i = 1;

while(i <= 5){
    console.log(i);
    i++;
}
```

---

## Increment

```javascript
